--- 
apiVersion: v1
data: 
  tls.crt: 
  tls.key: 
kind: Secret
metadata: 
  name: parts-web-secret
  namespace: default
type: kubernetes.io/tls

--- 
apiVersion: extensions/v1beta1
kind: Ingress
metadata: 
  name: tls-ingress-parts
spec: 
  rules: 
    - 
      host: partsunlimited.cloudns.biz
      http: 
        paths: 
          - 
            backend: 
              serviceName: parts-web
              servicePort: 80
            path: /
  tls: 
    - 
      hosts: 
        - partsunlimited.cloudns.biz
      secretName: parts-web-secret
